Welcome to The Investment House, LLC
The Investment House, LLC is dedicated to the long term growth of capital. We define long term growth as the increase of purchasing power after taxes and inflation. We believe this is best done by thoroughly examining the horizon of broad economic change; assessing the corporations most likely to benefit; and understanding the way in which such corporate opportunities should be valued now and into the long term future.
 


